review_text: Always a great place to hang out with toddlers and kids up to 6-7 and sneak in some adult conversation. Lovely mature trees and hedges - a reliable place for hunting snails. Mind that it's quite a bit windier now. The adjacent depot was knocked down and there's a pit taking it's place. If you focus on your kids and just look westward toward the handy CCI, you can almost forget about the surrounding construction.
Great Park for kids and birthday party.

(Translated by Google) A quiet and friendly place where you can bring the children to play in the park with their friends or even have a romantic picnic ... Etc.

(Original)
Un endroit tranquille et sympathique où on peut amener les enfants jouer au parc avec leurs amis ou eencore faire un pique-nique en amoureux... Etc.
